                    <h4 class="example-header">Leadership Opportunities for Students</h4>
                    <div class="example-content">
• Lead a study group or class project team
• Organize a campus event or fundraiser
• Start a student organization around a shared interest
• Volunteer to coordinate activities for a club or society
• Mentor younger students in your field
